      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IZZY LETTS (1) has a terrific record this track and trip with four wins and two placings from six starts. Comes off a (16.96) win last time, scoring by a neck in a Grade 5 over 300m at this track. Appeals as a leading chance in this. SKETCHY TOBY (2) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (19.91) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. One of the better chances. LIFE'S A BOUNTY (4) was out of the placings last time when eighth at Angle Park (31.35) but did record best time of the card when winning three back. Has a good winning strike rate at this journey. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Better than last start and can bounce back. VICTA CHRISSY (6) has a solid strike rate at this track and distance.",
